tid":1299334,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:54:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94e4f45daef750cb07af1c876c31ff62fe5790b0","tid":1299334,"uid":90883,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:54:59.000Z","msg":"做對了"},{"pid":"5b5bceb3941980e0532c9e33710baaf2c11e79a4","tid":1299334,"uid":1241,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:55:47.000Z","msg":"敵人反對的我們要擁護<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebf42f2bda7ca933f9b977973b80254d82f1fe22","tid":1299334,"uid":258696,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"c8213b5a6d32fbf471637c509c30905edd2b1408","tid":1299334,"uid":276548,"like":308,"dislike":0,"score":308,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:44:33.000Z","msg":"吹呀 係唔係都屈你搵外國勢力<br />\n而家名正言順咁搵仲好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:56:31.000Z","msg":"係唔係都屈人暴力，<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75fa00f8a34c93bd2055cf1af66fc905fc8a1b54","tid":1299334,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:56:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfa05939a0248c78ee27872c632a3be6e0b30123","tid":1299334,"uid":253981,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:59:13.000Z","msg":"肥佬黎正在下一局很大的棋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89662483a6ed7869b20085834ac9a741696c53dd","tid":1299334,"uid":47259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:00:50.000Z","msg":"咁快手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e71533d91b4197a0d85916412287bae08c03d911","tid":1299334,"uid":236538,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:00:58.000Z","msg":"絕不接受任何妥協<br />\n<br />\n政府已不能信任<br />\n<br />\n自由正被逐步侵蝕<br />\n<br />\n集中立即實行雙真普選<br />\n<br />\n持久戰我們必敗<br />\n<br />\n我要真&middot;雙普選！<br />\n<br />\n刻不容緩！！！"},{"pid":"1f4b2086bb3ca8e7f8671a2458685e4514264d36","tid":1299334,"uid":106070,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:02:13.000Z","msg":"邊撚個學者咁撚巴閉"},{"pid":"b36cc356ee0ab338de5c741f86733bee52dc71f1","tid":1299334,"uid":55010,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:02:25.000Z","msg":"到底中共可以有幾多神經挑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人而家怕你有牙，一早反左面"},{"pid":"eebb6b2ffedaf3bcfff92c0af7e5a58381ed3091","tid":1299334,"uid":47259,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"93ed7128e26a63aceef2d4bf701a708e7bdfe314","tid":1299334,"uid":66324,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:53:41.000Z","msg":"我唔明點解會有咁多所謂學者奶共"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:03:15.000Z","msg":"香港理工大學專業及持續教育學院講師陳偉強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc84e79b39bdcf0b3c6fdf17dce1a95751e029f9","tid":1299334,"uid":276274,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:03:36.000Z","msg":"睇白粉報馬上變道友"},{"pid":"a300322af813a802149e74d8e1c0c7035ca68928","tid":1299334,"uid":2617,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:03:40.000Z","msg":"東方係咪得陳偉強一個學者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e696f4f33e3f6c99759446d062756775573dc03","tid":1299334,"uid":234704,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:04:18.000Z","msg":"次次都係呢個學者&ldquo;香港理工大學專業及持續教育學院講師陳偉強&rdquo;，<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲有無其他學者呀，馬生<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d97893ab6d45c1cfa16e9af5f489e8b55e9214a9","tid":1299334,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:04:19.000Z","msg":"搞港獨？慳啲啦<br />\n<br />\n陳偉強 大學講師<br />\n<br />\n梁振英想趁支持香港獨立的聲音未成氣候，便及早去除禍根，他以去年的佔領行動為例，認為當初的發起人也只是隨興說說，能否成功，心中全然沒底，但因為未能於萌芽時大力遏止，結果才釀成日後之災。CY如此「先天下之憂而憂」，真是其情可憫，我見猶憐，難怪他要早生華髮，常常面帶愁容。<br />\n<br />\n蓋憂能傷肝，大可不必，港獨一事，不妨由他們說去，一切只能說不能做的事，我等何妨盤膝安坐，只當趣劇來看？慢說在經濟上、軍事上、水源上、人口結構上，香港都沒有獨立的本錢，即使此地擁有如新加坡般的條件，可以自成一國，也不見得有搞得起獨立運動的人，有的只是一幫雞鳴狗盜、烏合之眾，他們既無德也無才。常言道：「秀才造反，三年不成」，若讓這幫人造反，恐怕即使耗上三百年也難以成事。<br />\n<br />\n要搞獨立的不可能是建制中人，定然要從反對派中尋。環顧本地的反對陣營，卻多是寡廉鮮恥、敢做而不敢承擔之人。就以雨傘運動為例，當初不少人信誓旦旦，要實行公民抗命，完事後會自承罪責云云。到頭來，真願意自首的人，可能還不到參與者的千分之一。運動發起人「佔中三子」身為始作俑者，過去一年多來不斷組織、煽動佔領行動，結果也只願意承擔參與非法集會罪，連領導者的角色也不敢坦承，跟昔日那些甘願為理想「拋頭顱，灑熱血」的志士仁人，相去不可以道里計。革命從來不是請客吃飯，反對派中根本沒有具犧牲精神的人，不願犧牲的話，那搞個屁！反對派中也沒人能寫出深深打動群眾的文章，更沒人能講出極具感染力的演辭。革命需要的才華他們一一欠奉，這就想搞獨立，不如慳啲啦！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n專家陳偉強<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},{"pid":"ca7b0d5b2b4f056d830d083afa8046eaba0c7b57","tid":1299334,"uid":275010,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"c8213b5a6d32fbf471637c509c30905edd2b1408","tid":1299334,"uid":276548,"like":308,"dislike":0,"score":308,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:44:33.000Z","msg":"吹呀 係唔係都屈你搵外國勢力<br />\n而家名正言順咁搵仲好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:04:46.000Z","msg":"唔洗煩一次過俾佢地講L飽佢"},{"pid":"256a026f568f397c49a59afc9064096fc5afcba1","tid":1299334,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:05:20.000Z","msg":"百分報乜都話唔合格"},{"pid":"febd213be13433ad66f7c3eeb63eb1073294194c","tid":1299334,"uid":26332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:05:35.000Z","msg":"專家食屎啦.jpg"},{"pid":"9f642bba91d8704fe91056100792e805c59e845c","tid":1299334,"uid":111006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:05:39.000Z","msg":"收皮啦白粉報"},{"pid":"d1fd4f163f7bd721cce64c6463bf0c6f16f2ae51","tid":