港<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd1b1bb66b91620cee13e768669e0e08dd8049a5","tid":1299334,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:18:41.000Z","msg":"比人強姦要嗌唔好"},{"pid":"7d547f0f900c9e1ff32171a3d747d40ffb3270fc","tid":1299334,"uid":53172,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:18:54.000Z","msg":"Lee d 先叫學者<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1629084233856156&amp;id=1441041672660414\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1629084233856156%26id%3D1441041672660414&d=R%2BBR62t8sBL7FL0rmd5Y1TMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=5d2f62a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1629084233856156&amp;id=1441041672660414</a><br />\n<br />\n做學者唔該考牌先"},{"pid":"7067fb37e8c0d608952d637debc8119cdcd234cf","tid":1299334,"uid":51343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:19:02.000Z","msg":"邊個學者呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8294ed1523db9a850fbd1a9b1d26e4a89a48bfdb","tid":1299334,"uid":167658,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:19:05.000Z","msg":"陳偉強現為香港理工大學 專業及持續教育學院講師, 亦是東方日報專欄作家<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n［回帶］<br />\n<br />\n陳偉強指，自從早年兩鐵合作後，港鐵自此獨大，政府理應於監管工作方面做得很好，但結果是不時出現故障延誤，「令市民返工返學都返唔到」，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">他又不排除有港英餘孽「搞鬼」，埋下地雷炸彈。<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解咁嘅智力都做到大學講師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8928023361d0265909f01c1fcf34d43fdb0b52f0","tid":1299334,"uid":60563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:19:29.000Z","msg":"快到咁<br />\n證明做得岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b15744b512f614568f41a4124afa4194126d26a5","tid":1299334,"uid":194298,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:19:48.000Z","msg":"收皮啦陳教授"},{"pid":"61e2a719abe92d6d1d8fa6eeaab4b0d56e51063e","tid":1299334,"uid":253016,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:20:37.000Z","msg":"屈你係其次<br />\n主要係真心怕你搵外國幫手<br />\n支那共產黨就係想關埋門打仔"},{"pid":"44ed675d826e98a4812a045eba870d57df962554","tid":1299334,"uid":263221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:20:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"176c39bbe1e219b34c15127c4267e0104bcdcf22","tid":1299334,"uid":270286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:21:19.000Z","msg":"陳雲哭了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df170d95bb8d36fd93f8ed992463e809ce34868f","tid":1299334,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:22:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />黎智英收美國佬錢我小學 聽撚到依家"},{"pid":"c5635e6a8455ee5ba6423d218afb2901cb296d44","tid":1299334,"uid":257516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:23:23.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">毛主席：被敵人反對是好事而不是壞事</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我認為，對我們來說，一個人，一個黨，一個軍隊，或者一個學校，如若不被敵人反對，那就不好了，那一定是同敵人同流合污了。如若被敵人反對，那就好了，那就證明我們同敵人劃清界線了。如若敵人起勁地反對我們，把我們說得一塌糊塗，一無是處，那就更好了，那就證明我們不但同敵人劃清了界線，而且證明我們的工作是很有成績的了。 <br />\n《被敵人反對是好事而不是壞事》（一九三九年五月二十六日）"},{"pid":"e3944ac53a469ef1a8b0979f34e3b2a21bff5f67","tid":1299334,"uid":166474,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8294ed1523db9a850fbd1a9b1d26e4a89a48bfdb","tid":12993